org.eclipse.modisco.jee.ejbjar.EjbJar11
Interface DocumentRoot

public interface DocumentRoot

A representation of the model object 'Document Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Assembly Descriptor
  • Cmp Field
  • Container Transaction
  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Ejb Class
